OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1784899120
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 7 Aug to Fri 21 Aug
OL,6,FSettled and dry weather will probably
OL,7,Fdominate through much of August,
OL,8,Fespecially across the south. Some
OL,9,Fspells of rain are still likely at
OL,10,Ftimes, especially across northern and
OL,11,Fwestern areas. Although many areas may
OL,12,Fsee mainly dry weather for the much of
OL,13,Fthe period, occasional summertime
OL,14,Fthunderstorms are possible on some
OL,15,Fdays. Temperatures will very likely
OL,16,Fremain above normal, with potential
OL,17,Ffor further hot spells, particularly
OL,18,Fin the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
